Introduction:

This directory contains a Scala solution to the exercise 164 of
4clojure.

The file hierarchy:

default.nix          // this is useful for reproducible builds, you need nix installed on your system
SolutionProcess.org  // here I use Emacs org-mode to proceed towards the solution
SolutionProcess.pdf  // pdf version of the previous file
SolutionProcess.html // html version of the previous file
problem164scala/
  build.sbt          // dependencies
  .ensime            // autogenerated file for Emacs Scala mode
  project/         // sbt files
  src/             // src and tests here
  target/          // sbt files
   ...

Just run "sbt test" in problem164scala/ to validate the solution.
